contentfulPagePressRelease.title: Her Highness Sheikha Moza Bint Nasser Visits Qatar Foundation National Day Celebrations at Darb El-Saai

childMarkdownRemark.html:
Her Highness Sheikha Moza bint Nasser this evening visited the National Day festivities of Qatar Foundation (QF) at the Darb El-Saai celebration grounds.

Her Highness, Chairperson of QF, was taken on a tour of the educational activities being showcased at QF’s celebration tent by affiliated centers and members that are promoting a culture of excellence and innovation designed to engage the community.

During the visit, Her Highness interacted with children at a storytelling session on Qatari culture and heritage, as well as met youngsters within the sustainability section of QF’s tent.

The activities help meet QF’s objectives of instilling knowledge and learning from an early age and creating a foundation for the young generation to develop educational excellence and personal development towards great careers.

Her Highness, Chairperson of Qatar Foundation, was accompanied by Her Excellency Sheikha Al Mayassa bint Hamad Al Thani, Chairperson of the Qatar Museums Authority and Member of QF Board of Trustees, and His Excellency Salah bin Ghanem bin Nasser Al-Ali, Minister of Youth and Sports and Head of National Day Celebrations Committee.
